<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Form &amp; Pixel Arts Collective</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400;1,700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    html, body {
      height: 100%;
    }

    body {
      background: #ffffff;
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .circle {
      background: #1a1a1a;
      color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 50%;
      aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
      width: clamp(320px, 70vmin, 700px);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 15%;
      text-align: left;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .fp-logo {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 260px;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
      margin: 0 auto 2em;
    }

    p {
      font-size: clamp(0.75rem, 1.3vw, 0.95rem);
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 1em;
    }

    p:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    strong em,
    em strong {
      font-weight: 700;
      font-style: italic;
      text-decoration: underline;
      text-underline-offset: 3px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="circle">
    <img class="fp-logo" src="/about/formandpixel/logo-white.png" alt="Form &amp; Pixel Arts Collective" />
    <p>Form &amp; Pixel Arts Collective champions a wide array of creative services, including acrobatic instruction with <strong><em>Duo Coalesce</em></strong>, and unique pottery creations from <strong><em>Thistle Jar</em></strong>.</p>
    <p>At the heart of our collective, Form &amp; Pixel not only captures life's moments through stunning <strong><em>photography</em></strong> but also innovative <strong><em>product design</em></strong>, merging aesthetics with functionality.</p>
    <p>Our commitment to creativity is not confined to these domains. We're continuously exploring and embracing new artistic endeavors, pushing the boundaries of what's possible.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
